The paper discusses data security in cloud computing, which is a topic covered in the sub-category of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses data access and costs in the pay-as-you-go paradigm, which are topics covered in the sub-categories of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
